traffic_model

Class Storage

  • java.lang.Object
    • traffic_model.Storage

  • public class Storage
extends java.lang.Object
    Stores large data sets used by the application. Includes map/road network data and statistical results of the model. This class is a singleton to allow easy access by multiple classes.
    Author:
    Daniel Bane
